fit and forward the action in terms of getting

00:03:49.599 --> 00:03:54.219
you where you want to go and which foods are
guaranteed to derail the action and take you

00:03:54.219 --> 00:03:56.239
exactly where you don't want to be.

00:03:56.239 --> 00:04:01.859
See, people have been victimized by the conventional
wisdom, which is both not really conventional

00:04:01.859 --> 00:04:06.010
when you look at the long range and certainly
not wise, which is that weight loss is simply

00:04:06.010 --> 00:04:07.489
a matter of calories and exercise.

00:04:07.489 --> 00:04:09.709
We eat too much, and we don't move enough.

00:04:09.709 --> 00:04:10.909
That's the conventional wisdom.

00:04:10.909 --> 00:04:12.900
It's been passed down for ages.

00:04:12.900 --> 00:04:17.780
Everybody believes it, including obese people,
and they think that if they're, in fact, fat,

00:04:17.780 --> 00:04:20.590
it's because they don't exercise enough and
they eat too much.

00:04:20.590 --> 00:04:25.770
That has a germ of truth, but you could drive
a Mack truck through the hole that's missing

00:04:25.770 --> 00:04:26.770
